  "texts": [
    "Research in cultural influences on the requirements elicitation process is scarce in the literature.",
    "Our research aims to fill this gap.",
    "Thus, we formulated the following research questions: RQ1: Does culture influence the requirements elicitation process?",
    "RQ2: How does culture influence the requirements elicitation process?",
    "In this phase the multicultural requirements elicitation framework (McRE) was developed based on i) the work by work of Hofstede (1980; 2001), Schein (1985), Spichkova et al. (2021), Alsanoosy et al. (2018; 2020), Hanisch et al. (2001), Jaakkola (2012), and Thanasankit et al. (2000)."
  ],
